              plain_text: "After tracing more of the winding streets of the historic ward we sauntered our way across the speedway and, quite literally, onto the Grand Prix track as our foot path into the Monte Carlo Quarter! (Watching out for speeding motorcycles). Passing the enormous grandstands (visible in the panorama below) we could almost hear the roar of the crowds and the whine of the engines that would be screaming through these streets in 5 days! ",
