              plain_text: "The small and very dense town drapes over a steep escarpment completely encrusted with homes, shops, pied-à-terres, streets and public spaces. Since traffic is jammed, walking turns out to be the best means of getting around even if we'd preferred otherwise—but what a workout. At one point during our ascent we were startled to overlook the back side of a five story apartment down a chasm only twenty feet wide!",
