              plain_text: "Aside from the copious sights along the way, our destination is the famed Place du Casino and Hôtel de Paris Monte-Carlo. Built by Prince Charles III and designed by Gobineau de la Brétonnerie in 1862 as part of the scheme to fill the coffers of the principality by draining the purses of Europe's wealthy gamblers.",
