              plain_text: "The edifice is small by Las Vegas standards but similarly constructed of mostly inexpensive materials contrived to create an opulent and theatrical impression—in this case in a baroque or rococo style, veritably dripping with decoration and detail in cement plaster, terra cotta, paint, copper and splashes of stone work—a pleasant assault on the senses!",
